# Class-06
Version Control Systems

learning about the version control system. Very important for those who write code because you can record versions in stages and it is very difficult to lose everything, it helps to control versions. Example: git hub 

Task

configure git through VSC, use the commands add, commit, push, pull. Then create directories to insert tasks, scripts, codes

# Class-07
Virtualization

I learned the concepts of virtualization, which consists of creating labs (virtual computers) for testing. Very important for cybersecurity since it has to deal with many operating systems, test versions and see vulnerabilities.

